article.headline: Cornell 83, Siena 77
article.story: ITHACA, N.Y. (AP) -- Louis Dale scored 20 points and had nine rebounds to lead Cornell in an 83-77 win over Siena Sunday. Ryan Wittman scored 14 points and had 11 rebounds, Collin Robinson contributed 14 points, and Adam Gore and Brian Kreefer each added 10 for Cornell (3-1). Alex Franklin had 19 points and 13 rebounds to lead Siena. Edwin Ubiles added 17 points, Kenny Hasbrouk scored 16 and Ronald Moore had 10 for Siena (2-3). Cornell shot 55 percent from the floor.
